  x.number <- length(x)
  x.sum    <- sum(x)
  x.sum/x.number
}

sum.row  <- function(x){
  sum.r <- NULL
  for(i in 1:nrow(x)){
    sum.r <- c(sum.r,sum(x[i,]))
  }
  sum.r
}

bmi <- function(height,weight){
  bmi.x <- round(weight/(height^2),2)
  if(bmi.x < 18.5){
    list(bmi=bmi.x,def="")
  }else if( bmi.x<24  ){
    list(bmi=bmi.x,def="")
  }else if( bmi.x<27  ){
    list(bmi=bmi.x,def="")
  }else if( bmi.x<30  ){
    list(bmi=bmi.x,def="")
  }else if( bmi.x<35  ){
    list(bmi=bmi.x,def="")
  }else{
    list(bmi=bmi.x,def="")
  }
}

factorial.for <- function(n){ 
  f <-1 
  if(n<2){
     return(1)
   }  
   for(i in 2:n){ 
     f <-f*i 
  } 
  f 
} 

factorial.while <-function(n){ 
  f <-1 
  t <-n 
  while(t>1){ 
    f <-f*t 
    t <-t-1 
    } 
  return(f) 
} 

factorial.for(5);factorial.while(5)
factorial.for(0);factorial.while(0)
